title: Little Green Cars Early & Unreleased
description:
Some early and unreleased songs by the band Little Green Cars found in the dark crevices of the Internet and on YouTube. YouTube rips are noted. Some song quality is better than others, these are the best versions I could find. I am missing their first EP, Volume I, and two songs off their second EP, Volume II. I can't find them anywhere, but such is life. These are songs that are "out of print" and impossible to purchase. Please purchase albums to support the artist!
